OL,3,CChristian school worker sacked over
OL,4,CLGBT+ posts wins appeal
OL,6,FA Christian school worker who was
OL,7,Fsacked after sharing social media
OL,8,Fposts criticising plans to teach about
OL,9,FLGBT+ relationships in schools has won
OL,10,Fa Court of Appeal battle.
OL,12,FKristie Higgs lost her role as a
OL,13,Fpastoral administrator and work
OL,14,Fexperience manager at Farmor's School,
OL,15,Fin Fairford, Gloucestershire, in 2019.
OL,17,FThe decision came after she shared and
OL,18,Fcommented on posts which raised
OL,19,Fconcerns about relationship education
OL,20,Fat her son's Church of England primary
OL,21,Fschool.
