OL,6,FPupils were to learn about the No
OL,7,FOutsiders In Our School programme, a
OL,8,Fseries of books that teaches the
OL,9,FEquality Act in primary schools.
OL,11,FMrs Higgs, who posted on a private
OL,12,Fpage under her maiden name, shared two
OL,13,Fposts in October 2018 to about 100
OL,14,Ffriends, one of which referred to
OL,15,F"brainwashing our children".
OL,17,FThe school received an anonymous
OL,18,Fcomplaint leading to Mrs Higgs'
OL,19,Fsuspension, and dismissal for gross
OL,20,Fmisconduct following a disciplinary
OL,21,Fhearing.
